{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/como-formatear-currencies-en-es6/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Ahora puedes utilizar la instancia <code class=\"language-text\">NumberFormat</code> para formatear cualquier número en un valor monetario.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en-US'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> style<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'currency'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> currency<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'USD'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// '$100.00'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"entendiendo-los-parámetros\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#entendiendo-los-par%C3%A1metros\" aria-label=\"entendiendo los parámetros permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Entendiendo los parámetros</h2>\n<p>Hablemos de los parámetros. Se compone de los <code class=\"language-text\">locales</code> y el objeto <code class=\"language-text\">options</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>locales<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"locales\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#locales\" aria-label=\"locales permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Locales</h3>\n<p>Este es la configuración del lenguaje y la región. Está hecho del código del lenguaje y el código del país.</p>\n<p>Por ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">en-CA\n\nen = English (lenguaje)\nCA = Canada (país)\n\nes-PE\n\nes = Español (lenguaje)\nPE = Perú (país)</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h3>\n<p>Hay muchas opciones, pero hablemos de tres en especial: <code class=\"language-text\">styles</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">currency</code> y <code class=\"language-text\">minimumFractionDigits</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style\" aria-label=\"style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style</h4>\n<p>Es la parte fácil. Este es el estilo para su formato de número. Dado que este es un post sobre currencies, nuestra elección sería <code class=\"language-text\">currency</code>. Los 3 valores posibles son:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>decimal (formato numérico simple, el por defecto)</li>\n<li>currency (formato de moneda, lo que queremos usar ahora)</li>\n<li>percent (formato de porcentaje)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> money <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en-US'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> currency<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'USD'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  style<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'decimal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>money<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// '100'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en-US'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> currency<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'USD'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  style<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'currency'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>money<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// '$ 100.00'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en-US'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> currency<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'USD'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  style<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'percent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>money<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// '10,000%'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"currency\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#currency\" aria-label=\"currency permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Currency</h4>\n<p>Obviamente, hay muchas opciones de monedas. </p>\n<p>He aquí algunos ejemplos:</p>\n<p>CAD (dólar canadiense)\nUSD (dólar estadounidense)\nEUR (euro)\nCNY (RMB chino)\nPEN (soles)</p>\n<h4 id=\"minimumfractiondigits\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#minimumfractiondigits\" aria-label=\"minimumfractiondigits permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>minimumFractionDigits</h4>\n<p>El número mínimo de dígitos de fracción a utilizar. Los valores posibles van de 0 a 20; el valor por defecto para el formato de números y porcentajes es 0; el valor por defecto para el formato de moneda es 2.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"en-US\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tstyle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"currency\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  currency<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"USD\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  minimumFractionDigits<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// '$ 100'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"recursos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#recursos\" aria-label=\"recursos permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Recursos</h2>\n<p>Para más información puedes revisar los siguientes links:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\">Intl.NumberFormat - JavaScript | MDN</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat/NumberFormat#parameters\">Intl.NumberFormat() constructor - JavaScript | MDN</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.currency-iso.org/en/home/tables/table-a1.html\">Current currency &#x26; funds code list</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Ahora puedes utilizar la instancia  para formatear cualquier número en un valor monetario. Entendiendo los parámetros Hablemos de los…","fields":{"slug":"/como-formatear-currencies-en-es6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Cómo formatear currencies en ES6","date":"March 20, 2021","tags":["JavaScript","NumberFormat"],"description":null,"banner":"https://i.imgur.com/D9SPorK.png","slug":"como-formatear-currencies-en-es6"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/como-formatear-currencies-en-es6/","previous":{"id":"72ecf164-b2ba-52a0-90a9-2845dde5c306","frontmatter":{"title":"Cómo orar por nuestros líderes políticos","banner":"https://i.imgur.com/6KkHj67.jpg","categories":["JesusFreak"],"tags":["oración","política"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/como-orar-por-nuestros-lideres-politicos/"}},"next":{"id":"6992bb22-7eb5-5058-81db-87036a710382","frontmatter":{"title":"Revertir / Deshacer un commit de un Gist","banner":"https://i.imgur.com/qvcdlok.png","categories":["Code"],"tags":["git"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/revertir-deshacer-un-commit-de-un-gist/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}